4-3573882">在新奥尔良爵士音乐节上演出</a>。其他演出预计将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-announce-stacked-line-up-for-2024-3545261">Primavera Sound</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/vampire-weekend-the-postal-service-and-lcd-soundystem-to-headline-kilby-block-party-2024-3554756">Kilby Block Party</a>举行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-vampire-weekends-bold-new-singles-capricorn-and-gen-x-cops-3588544">查看《Vampire Weekend》大胆的新单曲“Capricorn”和“Gen-X Cops”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
万代南梦宫悄然退出五款游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bandai-namco-quietly-quits-on- Five-games-3588537?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bandai-namco-quietly-quits-on- Five-游戏Ali ShutlerFri, 16 Feb 2024 11:42:57 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3588537 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>工作室今后将采取更严格的质量控制</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bandai-namco-quietly-quits-on-five-games-3588537">万代南梦宫悄然退出五款游戏的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/bandai-namco-studios@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bandai-namco">万代南梦宫</a>证实，它最近取消了至少五款正在开发的游戏。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/tekken-8-review-3575505">《铁拳 8》评论：从零到英雄</a></strong></li></ul><p>万代南梦宫在最近的一份财务报告中证实，过去 12 个月其数字部门的销售额下降了 8.9%，收入下降了 96.5%。</p><p>在谈到结果时（通过<em><a href="https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/bandai-namco-reveals-it-recently-cancelled-five-games-saying-it-plans-stricter-quality-control/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VGC</a></em> ），该公司表示，由于工作室“停止开发至少五款正在开发的其他游戏”，他们“记录了处置损失”。废除这些头衔的决定是“根据有关评估的内部规则”做出的。</p><p>万代南梦宫接着表示，它正在寻求“建立一个最佳且平衡的游戏组合”，并将“仔细”检查他们的开发系统。</p><p>他们补充说：“我们将加强发展，注重质量。” “我们改变了开发结构，制定了更严格的开发标准，缩小了标题范围，并改变了开发费用的记录方法。与之相关的技术研究费用高于年初的预期。” </p><figure id="attachment_3171270" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3171270" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3171270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2.jpg" alt="埃尔登之戒" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/Elden-Ring-screenshot-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3171270" class="wp-caption-text"> 《埃尔登之戒》。图片来源：FromSoftware</figcaption></figure><p>万代南梦宫还解释说，收入下降的很大一部分原因是<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/elden-ring">《Elden Ring》</a></em>的成功，该游戏于 2022 年 2 月发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-has-sold-over-20-5million-copies-since-launch-3442746">销量超过 2050 万份</a>，但该工作室无法在其他游戏中复制其受欢迎程度。</p><p> “由于游戏的开发周期较长，从投资到收回成本的时间也在拉长，”他们继续说道。 “除了缩小游戏范围之外，我们还在考虑通过分类来优化我们的游戏的最佳方式，例如战略性的全球游戏和适合轻度用户的休闲游戏。”</p><p>不过，万代南梦宫补充说，最近发布的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/tekken-8">《铁拳 8》</a></em>已经证明在财务上取得了成功。 “至于正在开发的游戏阵容，我们正在为<em>《Elden Ring》</em>和新的<em>《龙珠》</em>游戏准备大规模的下载内容，所以请大家期待这些游戏。”</p><p>上周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/fromsoftware">FromSoftware</a>表示正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/elden-ring-devs-working-hard-on-dlc-but-there-are-still-no-release-plans-3585144">“努力”开发<em>《Elden Ring》</em>的扩展包</a>，但尚未确认发布窗口。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bandai-namco-quietly-quits-on-five-games-3588537">万代南梦宫悄然退出五款游戏的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
